# 01 Basics

This section covers the Python fundamentals that form the foundation for every project in this repository.

Although these examples are relatively simple, they introduce concepts that will be used repeatedly throughout later networking, automation and cybersecurity projects.

---

## Topics

Examples may include:

- Variables
- Data Types
- Operators
- Conditional Statements
- Loops
- Functions
- Modules
- Classes
- Exception Handling

---

## Goal

Develop a strong understanding of core Python concepts before applying them to cybersecurity and automation.

---

Scripts in this directory increase in difficulty as new concepts are learned.
